<!-- snippets/page-shipping-delivery-custom.liquid -->
<div class="ga-shipping-page-wrapper" style="padding: 2rem 0; font-family: var(--ga-font-family-sans);">
  
  <!-- Editorial Page Header -->
  <div class="ga-shipping-header-editorial" style="text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 4rem auto 6rem auto; border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--ga-border-color); padding-bottom: 4rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; padding-right: 1.5rem;">
    <span class="ga-subtitle" style="color: var(--ga-gold-cream); font-size: 1.3rem; letter-spacing: 0.3em; font-weight: 700;">SAFE & ASSURED LOGISTICS</span>
    <h1 class="ga-title" style="font-size: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 4.4rem); font-family: var(--ga-font-family-serif); margin-top: 1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; color: var(--ga-forest-green);">Shipping & Delivery Policy</h1>
    <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.6rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--ga-dark-text); font-weight: 300; max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto;">
      From the pristine, high-altitude cooperatives of the Himalayas to your home, we ensure that every jar of pure A2 Bilona Ghee travels safely under controlled conditions.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Main Text-Based Policy Content -->
  <div class="ga-shipping-content-block" style="max-width: 750px; margin: 0 auto 6rem auto; padding: 0 1.5rem;">
    
    <!-- Section 1 -->
    <div style="margin-bottom: 4.5rem;" class="ga-reveal">
      <h2 class="ga-title" style="font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-family: var(--ga-font-family-serif); color: var(--ga-forest-green);">1. Delivery Timelines & Charges</h2>
      <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.55rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--ga-dark-text); font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        We offer standard shipping across India. Every order is carefully processed, hand-inspected, and dispatched from our facilities within <strong>24 to 48 hours</strong> of order placement.
      </p>
      <ul style="list-style-type: none; padding-left: 0; margin-top: 1.5rem; font-family: var(--ga-font-family-sans); font-size: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--ga-dark-text);">
        <li style="margin-bottom: 1.2rem; padding-left: 2rem; position: relative;">
          <span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--ga-gold-cream);">✦</span>
          <strong>Complimentary Shipping:</strong> Free delivery is automatically applied at checkout to all orders valued at <strong>₹1,499 and above</strong>. For orders below ₹1,499, a flat shipping fee of ₹99 is applicable.
        </li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 1.2rem; padding-left: 2rem; position: relative;">
          <span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--ga-gold-cream);">✦</span>
          <strong>Metro Cities:</strong> Deliveries to major metropolitan zones (including Delhi-NCR, Mumbai, Bangalore, Chennai, Kolkata, and Hyderabad) are typically completed within <strong>3 to 5 business days</strong> after dispatch.
        </li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 1.2rem; padding-left: 2rem; position: relative;">
          <span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--ga-gold-cream);">✦</span>
          <strong>Rest of India:</strong> For Tier-2/Tier-3 cities, regional hubs, and remote mountainous sectors, standard transit times range between <strong>5 to 7 business days</strong>.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 2 -->
    <div style="margin-bottom: 4.5rem;" class="ga-reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
      <h2 class="ga-title" style="font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-family: var(--ga-font-family-serif); color: var(--ga-forest-green);">2. Eco-Conscious Glass Packaging</h2>
      <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.55rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--ga-dark-text); font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        To preserve the organic purity, delicate mountain aroma, and granular texture of our wood-fired A2 Ghee, we store it exclusively in food-grade glass jars. Glass is chemically inert, preventing any taste alteration or chemical leaching associated with plastic containers.
      </p>
      <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.55rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--ga-dark-text); font-weight: 300;">
        We secure these fragile jars using custom-molded, multi-layered 5-ply corrugated cardboard shells designed to absorb high impacts during transit. True to our sustainable Himalayan philosophy, **our entire shipping kit is 100% plastic-free and fully recyclable**.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 3 -->
    <div style="margin-bottom: 4.5rem;" class="ga-reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.15s;">
      <h2 class="ga-title" style="font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-family: var(--ga-font-family-serif); color: var(--ga-forest-green);">3. Climate Stability during Transit</h2>
      <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.55rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--ga-dark-text); font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
        Traditional wood-fired Bilona Ghee has a stable molecular arrangement rich in short and medium-chain fatty acids. Because of its authentic slow-simmered preparation, it naturally resists spoilage even under varied climate conditions.
      </p>
      <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.55rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--ga-dark-text); font-weight: 300;">
        As your shipment travels across different regional temperature zones, the ghee may experience minor changes in state (partial melting or solidification). This transition is completely natural and does not alter the product's medicinal values, taste, or shelf life.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Section 4 -->
    <div style="margin-bottom: 4.5rem;" class="ga-reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
      <h2 class="ga-title" style="font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-family: var(--ga-font-family-serif); color: var(--ga-forest-green);">4. Cash on Delivery (COD)</h2>
      <p class="ga-body" style="font-size: 1.55rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--ga-dark-text); font-weight: 300;">
        Cash on Delivery service is available for most postal codes in India. A standard convenience surcharge of ₹49 is applied to COD orders at checkout to support processing logistics. COD packages follow the identical processing times and shipping timelines as prepaid orders.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- FAQ Section (Single Column Text Layout) -->
  <div style="max-width: 750px; margin: 0 auto 6rem auto; padding: 0 1.5rem; border-top: 1.5px solid var(--ga-border-color); padding-top: 5rem;">
